#: ..\..\modeling\meshes\editing\duplicating\mirror.rst:21
msgid ""
"Mirroring an Object or Mesh selection will create a reversed version of the "
"selection. The position of the mirrored version of the selection is "
"determined by the *Pivot Point.* A common use of mirroring is to model half "
"an object, duplicate it and then use the mirror transform to create a "
"reversed version to complete the model. Note that mirrored duplicates can "
"also be created with a *Mirror modifier.*"
msgstr ""
"镜射一个对象或网格会产生原结构的反转体。反转结构的位置将由 *轴心点* 决定。镜"
"射的常见用法是制作出物体的一半将其复制并使用镜射变换来产生一个反转结构来完成"
"这一模型。注意复制镜像还可以通过 *镜射修改器* 来产生。"

#: ..\..\modeling\meshes\editing\duplicating\mirror.rst:34
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "使用方法"

#: ..\..\modeling\meshes\editing\duplicating\mirror.rst:36
msgid "To mirror a selection along a particular global axis press:"
msgstr "要沿着指定的轴向镜射选中结构需按下："

#: ..\..\modeling\meshes\editing\duplicating\mirror.rst:39
msgid ":kbd:`Ctrl-M`, followed by :kbd:`X`, :kbd:`Y` or :kbd:`Z`."
msgstr "`Ctrl-M`，然后按下`X`，`Y`或`Z`。"

#: ..\..\modeling\meshes\editing\duplicating\mirror.rst:42
msgid ""
"The image *Mirroring a selection* shows the results of this action after a "
"mesh element has been duplicated."
msgstr ""

#: ..\..\modeling\meshes\editing\duplicating\mirror.rst:48
msgid ""
"In Mesh mode, you can mirror the selection on the currently selected "
"Transform Orientation by pressing the appropriate axis key a second time. "
"For example, if the Transform Orientation is set to *Normal*, pressing:"
msgstr ""
"网格模式下，你可以通过按下2次轴向键来沿着已选择的变换坐标系镜射选中结构。例"
"如，若变换坐标系设置为 *法线* ，按下："

#: ..\..\modeling\meshes\editing\duplicating\mirror.rst:53
msgid ":kbd:`Ctrl-M`, followed by :kbd:`X` and then :kbd:`X` again"
msgstr "`Ctrl-M`， 然后按下`X`并再次按下`X`，"

#: ..\..\modeling\meshes\editing\duplicating\mirror.rst:56
msgid ""
"will mirror the selection along the X-axis of the *Normal Orientation.*"
msgstr "将会沿着 *法线坐标系* 的x轴来镜射选中结构。"

#: ..\..\modeling\meshes\editing\duplicating\mirror.rst:63
msgid "Interactive mirror."
msgstr "交互式镜射"

#: ..\..\modeling\meshes\editing\duplicating\mirror.rst:68
